            "description": "<div class=\"article_content line_1_5em\">\n<div id=\"upper\"><p>山高控股<a class=\"color_mpf\" href=\"stock1.php?code=0412\"><strong>（0412）</strong></a>今早股價插水，最多曾跌57.3%，低見5.98元，現報6.21元，仍跌55.7%，暫成交6.93億元。</p></div>\n<div id=\"lower\"><div class=\"articlelogin\">\n<p>該股昨被證監會點名股權高度集中，街貨量僅7.54%。</p> </div></div>\n</div>",
